Data tabulator

Summary
Use the widgets on this page to explore the Pre-SA and Post-SA datasets. The first column includes the available variables from each dataset. Variables can be moved into the second column to position them as table rows or the y-axis of a plot, or into the header row to position them as table columns/x-axis. The two drop-down menu options allow choosing from several output formats and summary types. For details on how the datasets have been prepared from the raw data downloaded from Qualtrics™, see the Data Preparation Report.

Pre-SA dataset

Post-SA dataset

Variables that have been included in both surveys are colour-coded, with green for the pre-SA version and orange for the post-SA version.
